</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> Install in reverse order. 
</p></entry><entry colname="col3" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p "> 
</p></entry></row><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">2 
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" align="left" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Carry out the adjustments: 
</p><ul class="- topic/ul "><li class="- topic/li "><p class="- topic/p "><xref keyref="01ADJU007" class="- topic/xref " href="GUID-E30D0D63-1649-498E-8E93-E4D51B79CDB8.xml" format="dita" locktitle="yes" type="task"><?ditaot usertext?><?xm-replace_text 01 How to adjust the distance between the curing carriage and the...?>01 How to adjust the distance between the curing carriage and the printhead carriage</xref> 
